{"tid":1110100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問基督徒點睇【安心偷食】？","createTime":"2019-04-16T12:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:55:28.000Z","uid":191462,"like":76,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d35e4d0cc4f20b70895bf5b8de2e33474ae24121","tid":1110100,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"就我讀過幾年基督教學校嘅理解<br />\n呢個係咪上帝俾佢哋4位嘅考驗？<br />\n係咪向上帝懺悔就可以冇事？<br />\nSammi係咪應該要原諒佢哋？<br />\n因為我記得有人喺聖經講過耶穌話過你俾人車左一巴要俾人車埋右一巴<br />\n咁係咪應該讓咗安仔俾心穎？<br />\n馬明應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n「我對你說：不是到七次，乃是到七十個七次。」（馬太福音18:22)<br />\n<br />\n「不要跟邪惡的人對抗。有人摑你的右臉，就連左臉也轉過來讓他摑。」<br />\n（馬太福音5:39）<br />\n<br />\n利申：信佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a7d41789b6dda6f1b97d9700770859c668a0bd","tid":1110100,"uid":185990,"like":11,"dislike":50,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"水唔是咁抽的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09698f37bdede51cb8eb7d2381da2030c00871c0","tid":1110100,"uid":191462,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"f1a7d41789b6dda6f1b97d9700770859c668a0bd","tid":1110100,"uid":185990,"like":11,"dislike":50,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"水唔是咁抽的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaed5122b12c98c1e830a7cd124e9a0a79ea04dd","tid":1110100,"uid":242597,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"我個ex 信耶穌， 咪又係俾帽我帶? 最後我原諒佢， 佢番多左教會， 幾年後咪又係散， 而且帽機會好撚大"},{"pid":"499c6c1a2b0455e9f46d7e9c1cd5bd702bab6a27","tid":1110100,"uid":73573,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"首先可以屌足70個7次<br />\n<br />\n俾人打完左邊屎忽 要俾埋右邊屎忽人打<br />\n屌完西可以屌埋屎眼<br />\n<br />\n跟手去悔過食個五餅二魚<br />\n四個一齊食返餐聖餐 全部人天堂可照上"},{"pid":"3a803d69d0f5b18dfa2546d9e71